description: This Chainlink VRF common Parvati purrs with a rating of 54, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 108, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 2 for North, 3 for East, Stringalong for South, and Box for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/40542-23742-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [108 Votes, Common]
